messages.text:
Dear Representative Lee Hyung-soo,

Over the years of using Haru, and through the Luna and FTX incidents, I've come to trust that Haru is being managed very soundly.

Even after the lock-up was lifted, I left my crypto in Haru, trusting in it and hoping for its further growth and development.

However, Haru's sudden announcement of a withdrawal suspension yesterday is far from the image we have seen and expected.

I hope the claim that the evacuation was for the safety of the employees is true, and I would appreciate it if you could share the official position and recovery plan as soon as possible.

The funds of the investors are not only for weddings, education, children's education, rent, but also hard-earned money over the years. What's the difference between such a response overnight and a rug pull? I implore you to share even a recovery plan as soon as possible for problem solving. Even overseas Celsius and Hodlnaut, though it was difficult to return the assets immediately, did not delay in making legal responses and communicating with customers.

I hope it's not a big problem, and I hope you become a company representative who is not ashamed to your employees and customers.

messages.text:
[Guide] Haru Invest. Suspension of Withdrawal of Target Digital Assets and Notice
Registration date 2023.06.13 11:30|Views 11530
hello. Upbit is the most trusted global standard exchange.

Today, Haru Invest. announced an announcement regarding the decision to suspend deposit and withdrawal of digital assets as of 2023-06-13 (Tue) 09:40 (KST).
After the suspension of deposit and withdrawal of Haru Invest., activities such as community suspension have been confirmed, and Upbit plans to restrict the withdrawal of digital assets for Haru Invest. as part of investor protection measures, so please refer to the use of the service.

Note: Announcement on Suspension of Deposits and Withdrawals by Haru Invest.
[Notice]

Due to the nature of digital assets, once the withdrawal application is completed, it cannot be canceled. Keeping the above circumstances in mind, please be sure to check the sending address before applying for withdrawal.
Deposit/withdrawal support may change depending on the circumstances of Haru Invest. Please be careful with digital asset withdrawals targeting Haru Invest.
Upbit will always do its best to protect the safety of your assets.
thank you

ğŸ”¬âš ï¸ 13.06.2023: Temporary suspension of withdrawals: Analysis & Possible implications

â„¹ï¸ TL;DR: If only 1 trading partner has gone down, this could mean only up to 5% of the capital is exposed. Please read below for argumentation and wait for a official statement by Haru Invest.

Today it has been announced that Haru Invest is forced to suspend temporarily withdrawals and deposits.

The cited reason is â€œan issue with one of the partnersâ€. From previous deep dive investigations of Haru Invest (

) it has been identified that Haru Invest utilizes ~10 trading partners, which are all subject to strict scrutiny and investigation. Aside of that, reportedly, the company has 2 internal trading teams. The collaboration between the internal and external trading teams facilitates the development of new earning strategies (by utilizing some of the outside knowhow).

To come back to the issue, it is completely possible for one of the partners to have stopped operations / â€œgone rogueâ€ during recent pressure on Binance and in the US in general. This risk has been identified by our deep dive review of Haru Invest.

Now, the good news is that we personally think this is only 1 trader. Through our own investigation (and also by the words of Haru Invest officials and information on Haru Support) it has been stated that the user trading capital is split (almost) equally among the ~10 trading partners. Additionally, it has been confirmed that no less than 50% of the trading capital is traded by the 2 internal Haru Invest teams, leaving at most ~50% to be managed by the ~10 trading partners. If 1 of these partners have a problem, theoretically this would mean this is an up to 5% exposure from the total managed capital.

âš ï¸ NOTE: This analysis is done only based on publicly available and officially communicated information from Haru Invest team and Support pages. I am not a part of Haru Invest team and in no way affiliated or representing the company. If you have questions, please visit Haru Invest support and open a ticket (
